(26, 'Dr. Ashmeet Singh', 2, 'ANR Hospital', '4', 144001, 'Building Number 309, New Jawahar Nagar, Jalandhar, Landmark: Opposite Express Vegetarian & Near Guru Amar Dass Chowk, Jalandhar', '9582246745', 'ashmeets@gmail.com', 'https://www.asmeetanr.com', 'upload/doctors/ash.jpg', '10:00:00', '18:39:00', 'Dr. Ashmeet finished his MD in psychiatry in the year 2009 from the prestigious Manipal University. He joined this hospital in June 2009. He is a member of American Society of psychosomatic medicine. He attends regular OPD, IPD and also visiting psychiatrist in Modern Hospital, Hoshiarpur and Guru Nanak Mission Hospital, Dhahan Kaleran, Banga', ''),
(27, 'Dr. Pankaj Verma', 2, 'Verma Neurophsychiat', '5', 141001, '502 - L, Model Town, Landmark: Near Children Traffic Park, Ludhiana', '8443982367', 'pankajverma@yahoo.com', 'https://www.pankajverma.com', 'upload/doctors/verma.jpg', '09:00:00', '20:00:00', 'Dr. Pankaj Verma is a Psychiatrist in Model Town, Ludhiana and has an experience of 9 years in this field. Dr. Pankaj Verma practices at Verma Neurophsychiatry & De- Addiction Centre in Model Town, Ludhiana. He completed MBBS from B J Medical College Ahemdabad in 2007 and DPM (Psychiatry) from B J Medical College Ahemdabad in 2009.\r\nSome of the services provided by the doctor are: Drug Abuse,Drug Abuse & DeAddiction Therapy,Depression Treatment,Alcohol De-addiction Treatment and Anxiety Disorders Treatment etc.', '');
