(20, 'Heart transplant', 'upload/surgery/21.ashx', 'The first operation is harvesting the heart from the donor. The donor is usually an unfortunate person who has suffered irreversible brain injury, called \"brain death\". Very often these are patients who have had major trauma to the head, for example, in an automobile accident. The victim\'s organs, o'),
